reviewText: After watching volumes 2,3 and 4 first, I really wanted to see Volume 1. Ask and I shall receive, I got Volume 1 and I was told that this is a "pilot" to the Issues 2,3,and 4. Volume one featured some Cute girls, but they are better ones in future volumes, the stand out in this one is the Host, I noticed her in the other volumes, but this this one where she stands out more because of the other girls. I would like to see a Blu-Ray just featuring the host. With all that said I did have a good time with Volume one, the 3D was great, but there are prettier girls in later volumes (Erin from Volume 3 to be particular) I would recommend seeing this, but 2,3 and 4 are better!
